      "title": "Style Tags",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "Style Tags \u2014 Complete List (109 tags, 7 categories)\n\nGenre (28): pop, rock, jazz, electronic, classical, hip-hop, r&b, country, reggae, blues, folk, metal, punk, disco, funk, soul, indie, edm, house, techno, ambient, lo-fi, k-pop, j-pop, c-pop, latin, reggaeton, bossa nova\n\nMood (18): happy, sad, energetic, calm, romantic, melancholic, uplifting, dark, dreamy, aggressive, peaceful, nostalgic, hopeful, mysterious, playful, epic, chill, intense\n\nInstrument (20): piano, guitar, acoustic guitar, electric guitar, bass, drums, violin, cello, saxophone, trumpet, flute, synth, strings, orchestra, choir, 808, harp, organ, ukulele, harmonica\n\nTempo (8): slow, moderate, fast, very fast, ballad, uptempo, mid-tempo, groovy\n\nVocal (14): male vocal, female vocal, duet, choir, rap, whisper, powerful vocals, falsetto, soprano, baritone, tenor, alto, harmonies, a cappella\n\nEra (9): 80s, 90s, 2000s, modern, retro, vintage, 70s, 60s, futuristic\n\nProduction (12): cinematic, lo-fi, hi-fi, acoustic, electronic, live, studio, raw, polished, minimalist, layered, atmospheric\n\n\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
